**When [interest rates](../../../../Financial%20Markets/Fixed%20Income%20Securities%20Tools%20for%20Today's%20Markets/Chapter%202/Interest%20Rate%20Quotations.md) exceed income growth rates, existing debt grows relative to income because debt compounds more rapidly than income expansion.**

